title: Winning numbers drawn in 'Pick 3' game
maintext:
OKLAHOMA CITY (AP) _ The winning numbers in Tuesday evening’s drawing of the Oklahoma Lottery’s “Pick 3” game were:
3-1-3
(three, one, three)
